0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23583,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/26\/health-better-wealth\/","url_meta":{"origin":31869,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Blessings: Health is better than wealth for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Yasar al-Juhani reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is nothing wrong with being wealthy for one who fears Allah, yet good health is better than wealth for one who fears Allah, and cheerfulness is itself among the blessings.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2141\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35302,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/24\/love-allah-messenger-ahl-bayt\/","url_meta":{"origin":31869,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mahabbah: Love Allah, His Messenger, and Ahl al-Bayt","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 24, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLove Allah for the blessings by which He nourishes you, love me for the love of Allah, and love the people of my house for the love of me.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3789 Grade: Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19144,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/13\/mercy-unity-punishment-division\/","url_meta":{"origin":31869,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Unity: Mercy in unity, punishment in division","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said upon the pulpit, \u201cWhoever is not grateful for small things will not be grateful for large things. Whoever is not thankful to people is not thankful to Allah. Mentioning the blessings of Allah is gratitude,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40542,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/even-smallest-blessings\/","url_meta":{"origin":31869,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Allah asks about even the smallest blessings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, among the blessing you will be questioned about on the Day of Resurrection are the cool shade, fresh dates, and cold water.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2369 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"im